 In case we issue any other command for Setting or Getting the bootchain, we get an error on the Aurix console and the NVM persistency blocks are corrupted.
 This leads to invalid response from getNext bootchain in the subsequent power cycles due to which ORIN does not boot up. No NV block Corruption at NV API queries_x000D_
